ackdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5832497\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zai1705473299234_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zai1705473299234_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zai1705473299234_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cui1665702872738\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n               \n Properties of Windows Application Shells \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">For Windows applications, you can define a background image, title bar, and other properties of the application window.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cui1665702872738__section_w2303ab1b5b1_w2304ab1b5_w2305ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d521431e51\">Presentation Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cui1665702872738__p_d26270e1_d26271e1_d26272e1\">The following properties can be set using the Properties Inspector in the Application Shell Editor. They cannot be changed at runtime using ProcScript.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cui1665702872738__li_d13199e1_d13200e1_d13201e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"myt1665702689407.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/myt1665702689407.html\" title=\"Title displayed in the window title bar or browser tab when the application shell, form, or server page is run. If no title is specified, the object name is displayed.\">Title</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cui1665702872738__li_d13202e1_d13203e1_d13204e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyl1665702688770.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyl1665702688770.html\" title=\"Specifies the library containing the global objects used by the component or application shell. If no library is specified, the library defined for the application shell is used. Otherwise, SYSTEM_LIBRARY is used as the default.\">Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cui1665702872738__li_d13205e1_d13206e1_d13207e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"glg1665702714695.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/glg1665702714695.html\" title=\"Name of the menu bar initially displayed for the current form or application shell.\">Menu Bar</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cui1665702872738__li_d13208e1_d13209e1_d13210e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nnt1665702586853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nnt1665702586853.html\" title=\"Name of the pop-up menu object to display when the user clicks the mouse button in this component, entity, or field.\">Pop-up Menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cui1665702872738__li_d13211e1_d13212e1_d13213e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xtq1665702714794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtq1665702714794.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the panel that is displayed with the form or application shell at runtime.\">Panel</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cui1665702872738__li_d13214e1_d13215e1_d13216e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oat1665702714863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oat1665702714863.html\" title=\"Specifies a panel that is available for the duration of the application session, even if a panel has been specified for the current component, or a toolbar definition exists.\">Session Panel</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cui1665702872738__li_d13217e1_d13218e1_d13219e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"txw1665702714934.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/txw1665702714934.html\" title=\"Position of the panel for a form or application shell when displayed at runtime.\">Panel Position</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cui1665702872738__section_w2306ab1b5b3_w2307ab1b5_w2308ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d521431e134\">Window and Image Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cui1665702872738__p_d26276e1_d26277e1_d26278e1\">To edit window and background image properties, click\n                the More icon (<img alt=\"more\" class=\"image\" id=\"cui1665702872738__image_kln_bb1_d1c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/ellipsis.png?_LANG=enus\"/>) in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window/App</span> property.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Window Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Property Name</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColor</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kno1665702715076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kno1665702715076.html\" title=\"Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values: True (default) or False.\">Caption</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Caption</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fym1665702715516.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fym1665702715516.html\" title=\"Window property of an application shell that determines how the application window is closed.\">Close (CanClose) [APS]</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">CanClose</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dvg1665702715374.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dvg1665702715374.html\" title=\"Determines whether the application window is treated as a Microsoft Windows dialog box, so the window is not resizable.\">Dialog</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Dialog</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cwr1665702715216.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwr1665702715216.html\" title=\"Window property that determines whether the user can minimize the form or application window at run time, and enables the Minimize/Restore button in the title bar.\">Iconize (CanIconize)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">CanIconize</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qkn1665702715286.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qkn1665702715286.html\" title=\"Determines whether the user can maximize and restore the size of the form or application window using the Maximize/Restore button in the title bar.\">Maximize</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">CanZoom</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gqy1665702715592.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gqy1665702715592.html\" title=\"Determines whether all forms that are run in the application shell are maximized.\">Maximized Forms</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">MaximizedForms</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wjh1665702607394.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wjh1665702607394.html\" title=\"The MessageLine property determines whether the message line is displayed at the bottom of the application window. This is used to display non-obtrusive messages to the user.\">Message Line</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">MessageLine</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjr1676877187333.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjr1676877187333.html\" title=\"Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the window can be resized at runtime.\">Resizable (CanResize)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">CanResize</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hse1665702715007.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hse1665702715007.html\" title=\"Determines whether the Uniface Setup utility is available from the system menu in the title bar.\">Setup</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Setup</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ecw1665702715443.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecw1665702715443.html\" title=\"Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False.\">System Menu (SysMenu)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">SysMenu</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cui1665702872738__p_d26279e1_d26280e1_d26281e1\">The following properties apply to a background image, if specified. To edit them, click the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Image</span> tab in the Application Shell properties dialog.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Image Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Property Name</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackImage</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmv1665702611521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmv1665702611521.html\" title=\"This property determines how the data (text or image) is aligned in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Horizontal Alignment (Halign)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">HAlign</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvp1665702611605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvp1665702611605.html\" title=\"This property determines the vertical alignment of data (text or image) in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Vertical Alignment ( Valign)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">VAlign</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbd1665702611680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Hscale</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sup1665702611757.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sup1665702611757.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Vertical Scaling ( Vscale)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">VScale</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxe1665702611833.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" title=\"Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.\">Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cui1665702872738__table_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">PreserveAspect</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cui1665702872738__p_d26282e1_d26283e1_d26284e1\">Default values for BackColor, MessageLine, and image properties can be set using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Shell</span> setting in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gma1665702671256.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Shell</a><p>Sets the default window properties of the application shell.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5832497\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5832497\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Properties of Windows Application Shells Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Properties of Windows Application Shells For Windows applications, you can define a background image, title bar, and other properties of the application window. Presentation Properties The following properties can be set using the Properties Inspector in the Application Shell Editor. They cannot be changed at runtime using ProcScript. Title Library Menu Bar Pop-up Menu Panel Session Panel Panel Position Window and Image Properties To edit window and background image properties, click the More icon ( ) in the Window/App property. Table 1. Window Properties Property Technical Property Name Background Color (BackColor) BackColor Caption Caption Close (CanClose) [APS] CanClose Dialog Dialog Iconize (CanIconize) CanIconize Maximize CanZoom Maximized Forms MaximizedForms Message Line MessageLine Resizable (CanResize) CanResize Setup Setup System Menu (SysMenu) SysMenu The following properties apply to a background image, if specified. To edit them, click the Image tab in the Application Shell properties dialog. Table 2. Image Properties Property Technical Property Name Background Image (BackImage) BackImage Horizontal Alignment (Halign) HAlign Vertical Alignment ( Valign) VAlign Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) Hscale Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) VScale Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) PreserveAspect Default values for BackColor, MessageLine, and image properties can be set using the Shell setting in the usys.ini file. Related Links Shell Sets the default window properties of the application shell. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}